    "This was inspired by the original LoRA paper (Hu et al., 2021), where they only adapted the attention weights.",
    "A diverse selection of benchmarks is essential to evaluate performance degradation across similar tasks when modifying task-specific subspaces within LLMs.",
    "This study used two signification collections of benchmarks: Holistic Evaluation of Language Models (HELM; et al., 2023c) and the Beyond-the-Imitation-Game Benchmark (BIG-Bench; et al., 2023a).",
